item.description: +++ title = ‘A Moneysupermarket of Higher Education Is a Misuse of Data’ date = 2018-06-26T20:56:18+01:00 draft = true meta_img = “/images/image.jpg” tags = [“tags”] description = “Desc” hacker_news_id = “” lobsters_id = “” +++ We want students to be better informed about degree choices & the returns - today, we're officially launching a competition for tech companies to take graduate data & create a MoneySuperMarket for students, giving them real power to make the right choice.
